              {
                "type": "text",
                "text": " ",
                "style": {
                  "bold": true
                }
              },
              {
                "type": "text",
                "text": "\n\nHi, we built a Slack app to summarise long threads in channels: "
              },
              {
                "type": "link",
                "url": "https://www.buildwithforest.com/summarise-with-forest"
              },
              {
                "type": "text",
                "text": "\nWe built this using our product Forest ("
              },
              {
                "type": "link",
                "url": "http://buildwithforest.com/"
              },
              {
                "type": "text",
                "text": ") which allows developers to build workflows and connect APIs extremely fast. We are still early in our development and would love to chat with developers who think Forest could be useful for them and get feedback!"
              }
